Name: Halo
Description: Software Development Kit (SDK) to access the Halo RESTful API.

Endpoints.Name: Get Setting
Endpoints.Description: Get the fields that constitute the setting

Endpoints.Name: Get User Message
Endpoints.Description: Get a specific user alert message

Parameters.Name: function
Parameters.Description: The administrative function to be executed

Endpoints.Name: Add User to Team
Endpoints.Description: Add a member to a team

Endpoints.Name: Remove User from Team
Endpoints.Description: Remove a member from a team

Parameters.Name: team
Parameters.Description: The new group attribute values. This does not need to be a complete representation. Only attributes to be modified need to be specified. Omitted attributes will retain their current values.

Parameters.Name: property
Parameters.Description: The new property attribute values. This does not need to be a complete representation. Only attributes to be modified need to be specified. Omitted attributes will retain their current values.

Endpoints.Name: Add Sector Node
Endpoints.Description: Create and add a node to a sector

Endpoints.Name: Remove Sector Node
Endpoints.Description: Delete node from sector with index

Parameters.Name: sector
Parameters.Description: The new sector attribute values. This does not need to be a complete representation. Only attributes to be modified need to be specified. Omitted attributes will retain their current values.

Parameters.Name: user
Parameters.Description: The new user attribute values. This does not need to be a complete representation. Only attributes to be modified need to be specified. Omitted attributes will retain their current values.

Parameters.Name: node
Parameters.Description: The new node attribute values. This does not need to be a complete representation. Only attributes to be modified need to be specified. Omitted attributes will retain their current values.

Endpoints.Name: Add Access Key
Endpoints.Description: Create an access key for a user

Endpoints.Name: Get Team Projects
Endpoints.Description: Get a list of team projects

Endpoints.Name: Add Project to Team
Endpoints.Description: Add a project to a team

Endpoints.Name: Remove Project from Team
Endpoints.Description: Delete a project from a team

Endpoints.Name: Get Project Teams
Endpoints.Description: Get a list of project teams

Endpoints.Name: Add Sector to Project
Endpoints.Description: Add a sector to a project

Endpoints.Name: Remove Sector from Project
Endpoints.Description: Delete a sector from a project

Endpoints.Name: Get Project Sectors
Endpoints.Description: Get the sectors for a project

Endpoints.Name: Get Engines
Endpoints.Description: Get a list of registered engines

Endpoints.Name: Get Engine Nodes
Endpoints.Description: Get a list of nodes supported by the engine

Endpoints.Name: Get Engine Structures
Endpoints.Description: Get a list of node hierarchal relationship structures supported by the engine

Endpoints.Name: Get Extension Settings
Endpoints.Description: Get a collection of all settings for an extension

Endpoints.Name: Get Extension Setting
Endpoints.Description: Get a collection of fields that make up an extension setting

Endpoints.Name: Get Dispatchers
Endpoints.Description: Get a collection of system dispatchers

Endpoints.Name: Get Dispatcher Protocols
Endpoints.Description: Get a collection of all protocols for a dispatcher

Endpoints.Name: Get Firmwares
Endpoints.Description: Get a collection of registered firmware packages

CustomTypes.Name: Property Type
CustomTypes.Description: The class type of given property

CustomTypes.Name: Extra
CustomTypes.Description: Custom information in the form of a key value

CustomTypes.Name: Incident Detail
CustomTypes.Description: Representation of an details of an incident definition.

Fields.Name: name
Fields.Description: A convenient identifying name. This is a human assignable value for convenience and is not unique.

Fields.Name: cause
Fields.Description: A description of the conditions that would cause this alarm definition to become active.

Fields.Name: impact
Fields.Description: A description of the impacts that would result in this alarm definition becoming active.

Fields.Name: remedy
Fields.Description: A description of the remedy that would resolve this alarm definition if it becomes active.

CustomTypes.Name: Person State
CustomTypes.Description: The account state of a person

CustomTypes.Name: Access Key State
CustomTypes.Description: The state of a Persons Access Key

CustomTypes.Name: Access Key
CustomTypes.Description: Representation of an Access Key definition.

CustomTypes.Name: Extension State
CustomTypes.Description: The execution state of an extension

CustomTypes.Name: Incident Event Type
CustomTypes.Description: The type of event that occurred in an incident event
